Metadata.Title: No smoking
Metadata.Description: 47 – It is time to clear the air.  The president of the local Home Owner’s Association is running a reelection campaign to clean up the neighborhood, but there is a cloud of pollution taking over Whittleton Creek; smokers.   Some of the residents are causing a stink with the smoke, littering the streets, and bringing down property values. The HOA wants to make do on their campaign promise and maintain power. Eliminate the targets as you see fit. Good luck.
